text.tspan: - Widget roles are described in objects labels.
- Press Ctrl+O to open object properties panel
- To see objects in a tree, select Object->Objects in menu
- Press Ctrl+X to edit SVG elements directly with XML editor
Some widgets like Switch or Button are displaying one of many
groups that represent the possible states of the widget.
Since all groups need to appear in the same place, they overlap
and the drawing becomes hard to understand and maintain.
